## 📊 BẢNG TÓM TẮT CÔNG NGHỆ

| Layer | Công nghệ | Vai trò |
|-------|-----------|---------|
| 🖥️ Hạ tầng | AWS EC2 (2 nodes) | Cloud servers |
| 🐳 Container | Docker + Docker Swarm | Orchestration |
| 🔄 CI/CD | Jenkins + Jenkinsfile | Automation pipeline |
| 🎨 Frontend | React + Vite + Nginx | User interface |
| ⚡ Backend | FastAPI (Python) | REST API |
| 🗄️ Database | Supabase (PostgreSQL) | Data storage |
| 📦 Registry | Docker Hub | Image storage |
| 📊 Metrics | Prometheus / cAdvisor | Resource monitoring |
| 📋 Logs | Grafana Loki + Alloy | Log aggregation |
| 🔍 Traces | Grafana Tempo + OTLP | Request tracing |
| 📈 Dashboard | Grafana Cloud | Visualization |
| 🤖 ChatOps | Telegram Bot API | Notifications |
| 🧪 Load Test | k6 | Performance testing |

